                      <p style='margin:0 0 24px 0; font:14px/1.6 Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#6b7280;'>If the free plan covers your current needs, that's genuinely fine. Pro is for when you're bumping into the limits and need more room to operate.</p>

